    }The 6th International Symposium on Engineering and Natural SciencesNovember 19-21, 2019  Bangkok, ThailandOPEN  for submission !!The 2019 International Symposium on Engineering and Natural Sciences (ISEANS) will be held from November 19-21, 2019 in Bangkok, Thailand. The purpose of the conference is to bring the world's scholars, professionals, academics, students and more together for oral sessions, poster sessions, and networking opportunities to promote, share and discuss various subjects and developments in the field ofengineering and natural sciences.The conference features international keynote addresses and a farewell socializing event.Important DatesSubmission DeadlineJuly 25, 2019Notification of AcceptanceAugust 15, 2019VenueCentara Watergate Pavillion Hotel BangkokContact & InquiryISEANS SecretariatEmail: iseans@iseans.orgWebsite: www.iseans.org  

